title: Coaches' Corner: UMD Football's Curt Wiese
text:
Coaches' Corner: UMD Football's Curt Wiese 
By Zach Schneider October 16, 2015 Updated Oct 16, 2015 at 3:22 PM CDT 
Duluth, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- The University of Minnesota Duluth (UMD) football team is (4-2) this season after a 34-27 win at home over St. Cloud State, which was the main topic of discussion in this week's "Coaches' Corner" with head coach Curt Wiese. 
This conversation is part of the weekly show "Bulldog Country," which covers all things UMD and airs every Friday night at 6:30 p.m. on the My 9 Sports Network.
